(# Snake Cash Rush Summary) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (## Executive Summary) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Snake Cash Rush is a browser-based Snake game built under `games/snake/src` with) Tj
T* (Python-driven gameplay logic, a money-bill pickup theme, a polished modern interface, live) Tj
T* (score tracking, and a persisted best score. The game is self-contained, frontend-only, and) Tj
T* (runs locally through a simple static server.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (## Delivered Scope) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (- Classic Snake gameplay with continuous movement and keyboard controls) Tj
T* (- Cash-bill pickups that grow the snake and increase score) Tj
T* (- Best-score persistence through browser local storage) Tj
T* (- Start, live-play, and game-over states with clear overlay messaging) Tj
T* (- Modern glass-style HUD and responsive layout) Tj
T* (- Detailed getting started guide in `games/snake/README.md`) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (## Acceptance Criteria Status) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Page shows title, board, score, best score, and start flow: Verified) Tj
T* (2. Snake starts moving and continues automatically after run start: Verified) Tj
T* (3. Money-bill pickup grows snake, raises score, and respawns pickup: Verified) Tj
T* (4. Best score updates only on exceed and survives reload: Verified) Tj
T* (5. Collision ends the run and exposes restart path: Verified) Tj
T* (6. Game is implemented inside `games/snake/src`: Verified) Tj
T* (7. Interface uses a cohesive modern visual system: Verified) Tj
T* (8. Layout remains usable on narrow screens: Verified) Tj
T* (9. Getting started guide supports local run without missing steps: Verified) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (## Validation Evidence) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (- Static diagnostics passed for HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Python files) Tj
T* (- Local app served successfully from `games/snake`) Tj
T* (- Browser validation confirmed start state, live state, collision state, and restart path) Tj
T* (- Deterministic validation confirmed score increment from `0` to `10`, snake growth from 3) Tj
T* (to 4 segments, and best-score persistence across reload) Tj
T* (- Narrow-screen validation at `390x844` showed no horizontal overflow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (## Test Cases Executed) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Launch local static server and load `http://127.0.0.1:8000/src/`) Tj
T* (2. Verify initial UI elements and ready overlay are visible) Tj
T* (3. Start a run and confirm live-play state activates) Tj
T* (4. Force a valid pickup on the next step and confirm score, growth, and best-score update) Tj
T* (5. Advance until wall collision and confirm game-over state) Tj
ET
